name: Life (AgentXMan)
description:
Hello people

today i am back with a new game and this one is kinda short but its worth a try.

This is basically a simulation of real life but with a promising notice of parallel worlds, multiverse, etc

Have fun with the game and if you have any suggestions or feedbacks then pls do let me know and i will try to fix that issue :D

also if browser laggy then pls download!
